1.0.name: wordpress/pandora
1.0.description: Customisable theme by Belicza.com. This theme contains integrated drop-down menu and slider. Pandora has 4 post listing view for index page and theme contains blog style, portal style and clan page style, and Pandora has special admin setup page for many options.
